transcript:
Customer: Namaskar.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Ha ji namaskar boliye.
Executive: Sarthak ji, very namaskar. Woh mein Shriya baat kar rahi thi Indiamart se.
Customer: Ji ji boliye.
Executive: Actually aapne concern raise kiya tha guidance ke liye Indiamart aapko.
Customer: Aapko jisko guidance karna hai na woh abhi hajar mein nahi hai.
Executive: Accha.
Customer: Hello. Available nahi hai woh available hoga toh mein phone karunga waisa bola tha madam.
Executive: Theek hai woh employee hai aapke?
Customer: Ha mera employee hai.
Executive: Koi nahi aapne account manager ko number de diya hai na free employee ka?
Customer: Account manager ka number nahi mera company ka number hai mein bhej dunga lekin woh available nahi hai abhi char panch din ke liye.
Executive: Nahi nahi subah baat hui thi na aap se toh aapne unko number aap mujhe number de dijiye mein char panch din ke baad unko connect kar lungi kyunki aapne concern raise kiya.
Customer: Mein mein jab woh available hoga na tab mein call karunga tab usko bitha ke samjha dena theek hai.
Executive: Theek hai mein whatsapp pe aapko hi bol deti hu theek hai aur mein apna naam number likh deti hu aap usi number pe call karna theek hai sir baki.
Customer: Theek hai mein usko bol dunga yeh number pe call karna kahin pe bhi dikkat rahe na toh.
Executive: Theek hai. Baki sir yeh jo aapne customer care pe call kiya tha na humse baat karne ke liye toh yeh yeh hum close kar rahe hain concern aapke mail pe ek bar aayega satisfied ka toh yes kar dena sir theek hai.
Customer: Okay okay.
Executive: Okay thank you.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer raised a concern for guidance.

Resolution:

- Executive offered to connect after 4-5 days.

- Executive will send a 'Hi' on WhatsApp.



Next Steps: 

- Customer will ask employee to call on the number.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Neutral -> Neutral



@@@Key Topics:

- guidance, employee, whatsapp, concern
